    <div class="container my-5">
        <div class="profile-header">
            <img src="~/img/consultant_profile1.jpg" alt="Consultant Image" class="profile-img">
            <div>
                <h2>John Smith</h2>
                <p class="specialty">Nutritionist</p>
                <p class="experience">
                    John Smith is a certified nutritionist with over 10 years of experience
                    helping individuals achieve their health and fitness goals. His expertise includes
                    weight management, meal planning, and dietary counseling. John believes in a
